s into mortal danger for this important mission!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/0ceb373e8529123ae70b128ecdd7e82a.poster.avif?t=1773414931\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/0ceb373e8529123ae70b128ecdd7e82a.webm?t=1773414931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/0ceb373e8529123ae70b128ecdd7e82a.mp4?t=1773414931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>At its core Swag and Sorcery is an epic, ruthless adventure that both RPG and idle game fans will appreciate. There's also a sarcastic cat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/9e651b401e95967b292a1e130d58b772.poster.avif?t=1773414931\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/9e651b401e95967b292a1e130d58b772.webm?t=1773414931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/929010/extras/9e651b401e95967b292a1e130d58b772.mp4?t=1773414931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
